Description: Deepika Padukone is an Indian actress and model. She appears mostly in Hindi films, as well as Tamil and Kannada language films. Born to badminton player Prakash Padukone, she chose to become an actress.
Name: Deepika Padukone

Description: Sushmita Sen is an Indian actress and model. She was crowned Miss Universe 1994 by outgoing title holder Dayanara Torres of Puerto Rico at the 43rd edition of the Miss Universe Pageant
Name: Sushmita Sen

Description: Dia Mirza, nicknamed Dee is a Indian model and actress who appears in Bollywood films. The actress along with her boyfriend Sahil Sangha and good friend Zayed Khan has started her own production house
Name: Dia Mirza

Description: Priyanka Chopra, Miss World 2000 made her debut in Bollywood films with 'The Hero'. Born in Jamshedpur, the extremely beautiful, sensuous, hot model-cum-actress has achieved a lot in a short time. She is the only Indian in USA to have been selected at state level for the National opus Honour choir.
Name: Priyanka Chopra Jonas

Description: Diana Penty is an Indian model and actress who made her film debut in Homi Adajania's film Cocktail
Name: Diana Penty

Description: Kriti Kharbanda is an Indian film actress who appears in Kannada and Telugu films. She made her debut with the Telugu film, Boni
Name: Kriti Kharbanda

Description: Sweet and dainty Amrita Rao, from a Chitrapur Saraswat Brahmin family was always fascinated by acting. Her first modeling assignment was for Fairever fairness cream and within a couple of months, she became a model for many top brand companies and did nearly 35 ad films. Cadbury's Perk and Bru coffee ads offered her a platform to step into the film industry. The pretty lass debuted in the film 'Ab Ke Baras' (2002)
Name: Amrita Rao

Description: Kajal Aggarwal is an Indian film actress, who appears in Telugu, Tamil and Hindi films. Kajal made her film debut in the 2004 Bollywood film Kyun...! Ho Gaya Na and entered the Telugu film industry through the film Lakshmi Kalyanam.
Name: Kajal Aggarwal

Description: Vimala Raman is an Indian film actress, model and a trained Bharatanatyam dancer. She made her acting debut in the 2006 Tamil film Poi and went on to appear primarily in Malayalam and Telugu films.
Name: Vimala Raman

Description: Samantha Ruth Prabhu is an Indian film actress and model who appears in Telugu and Tamil films. Born to Malayali and Telugu parents, Samantha was brought up in Chennai and pursued a career in modeling during her late teens.
Name: Samantha Ruth Prabhu

Description: Lara Dutta Bhupathi is an Indian Bollywood actress and former Miss Universe. She made her Hindi debut in 2003 with the film Andaaz which was a box office success and won her a Filmfare Best Female Debut Award.
Name: Lara Dutta

Description: Rani Mukerji is an Indian film actress who works in Hindi movies. Born to the Mukherjee-Samarth family, she made her acting debut with a cameo appearance in the Bengali film Biyer Phool, on the insistence of her mother.
Name: Rani Mukherjee

Description: Her features, her smile and most of all the sweet innocence and charm on her face can make a young girl blush with shame.
Name: Madhubala

Description: With striking, sharp features and a killing gaze, she remains one of the most beautiful faces ever.
Name: Waheeda Rehman
